      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.117006814479828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、この子すごい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This girl really is amazing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.117006814479828,
      "endTime": 12.436485373973847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.383673481146493
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.383673481146493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、井川さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Igawa-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.41700681447983,
      "endTime": 15.942312967777255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.142312967777254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "こそばゆいな\n葵でいいよ、何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's kind of awkward.\nJust call me Aoi. What's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.142312967777254,
      "endTime": 19.33226753473282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.527048910799486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私と合わせて踊ってみない？\n井川さ――葵は上手いけど、周囲と合わせないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why don't we dance together?\nIgawa-sa――Aoi‚ you're a good dancer‚ but if you don't match with the people around you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.527048910799486,
      "endTime": 26.827048910799487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "バックダンサーって、そうじゃない？\nだから、私とやってみましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that's not what being a backup dancer is about‚ right?\nSo let's try it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.027048910799493,
      "endTime": 31.149452580156797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.35329572921892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……、でも僕は\nバックで踊る気なんてないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… but I\nhave no intention of dancing in the back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.35329572921892,
      "endTime": 35.175857994615036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "自由にやらせてもらうって約束で\nここに入ったからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I joined this place with the promise that\nI could do things my own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.38662906255226,
      "endTime": 38.75898743237953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 38.97209678457084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……？\n貴方、そんなんじゃデビュー出来ないわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What…?\nYou're not going to be able to debut if you keep acting like that‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.97209678457084,
      "endTime": 43.151461751917026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.342255425114466
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "デビュー？\nデビューすることがそんなに大事なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Debut?\nIs debuting that important?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.342255425114466,
      "endTime": 47.45465910400851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 47.6755887584478
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "当然じゃない\nだって私達は全員アイドルを目指して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it is.\nWe're all aiming to be idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6755887584478,
      "endTime": 52.96704002187553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "莉央はダンスしてる時に\nそんなことを考えているの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ do you really\nthink about things like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.40892209178112,
      "endTime": 56.92150706416271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 57.11573895182113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "僕は踊ると気持ちがいいからやってるだけだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I only dance because it feels good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.11573895182113,
      "endTime": 60.43635119165877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 60.636351191658775
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちがいいから、やってるだけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just because it feels good…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.636351191658775,
      "endTime": 64.32397021021346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 64.52397021021346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央のダンスはすごくちゃんとしてる\nでも、それだけじゃ響かないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your dancing is very clean‚ Rio.\nBut that's not enough to make an impact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.52397021021346,
      "endTime": 69.59306324686507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "心と体がバラバラなんだ\n莉央、踊ってても楽しくないんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your heart and body aren't connected.\nRio‚ you're not having fun when you dance‚ are you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.79063687688014,
      "endTime": 75.20791592961451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.39063687688017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.39063687688017,
      "endTime": 77.74961638814115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 77.94961638814115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――確かにそうかもしれない。莉央はいつも誰よりも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Maybe she was right. Rio always danced more than anyone else‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.94961638814115,
      "endTime": 81.58294972147448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "踊っていたが、それはダンスを楽しみたいからじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but it wasn't because she wanted to enjoy dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.58294972147448,
      "endTime": 85.36294976034121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――早くデビューしたい、という強迫観念に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――She was driven by an obsession with debuting quickly‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.58294972147448,
      "endTime": 88.64961638814114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "背中を押されて、ただがむしゃらにやっていただけだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and was just desperately pushing herself forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.64961638814114,
      "endTime": 92.28961653278175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 92.51628305480783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方が昨日言ったことの意味が\n分かった気がするわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I think I understand\nwhat you meant yesterday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.51628305480783,
      "endTime": 96.42709929511851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 96.8162830548078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "僕、何か言ったっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did I say something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8162830548078,
      "endTime": 98.26628303096594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98.46628303096594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_04-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "私のダンスは重たいって言ったでしょ\n……もしかして、忘れてたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said my dancing was heavy.\n…Don't tell me you forgot already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.46628303096594,
      "endTime": 104.20435571239294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 104.39961636429918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
